sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant AdminWeb
    participant API
    participant Noti as Notification
    Admin->>AdminWeb: Approve/Reject/Lock POI
    AdminWeb->>API: POST /api/poi-approval/{id}/action
    API->>Noti: Create notification to saler
    API-->>AdminWeb: Updated status + message
    AdminWeb-->>Admin: Refresh list/counts
